%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%% uminho/ese/schl-defaults.clo
%% NOVA thesis configuration file
%%
%% Customization for ESE-UMINHO (strings and cover)
